
// This Hyperlambda code executes a workflow action named "html-encode-body" by invoking a file located at "/misc/workflows/actions/misc/html-encode.hl". It passes an argument named "html" to the file, which is derived from the "body" node within the ".arguments" node.
execute:magic.workflows.actions.execute
   name:html-encode-body
   filename:/misc/workflows/actions/misc/html-encode.hl
   arguments
      html:x:@.arguments/*/body
